            *Globigerina eugubina* and *Parvularugoglobigerina eugubina*, which facilitate
            fine-scale correlation across marine basins globally. The Danian also marks
            significant shifts in sedimentology and geochemistry, including isotopic
            excursions indicative of oceanographic and climatic reorganization in the
